  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span class=\"GramE\"><em>@UUID[Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.monsterspack.Actor.BBmXyjTGHzBWKz6K]{琉克歐的非凡機仆Mighty Servant of Leuk-O}</em></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">是一臺具有非凡的力量，身高</span>10<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">尺的機器，以使用它的那位臭名昭著的軍閥命名，當有人駕駛時，它會變成一個活化</span><span class=\"GramE\">的構裝生物</span>。它的身軀由一種來歷不明的黑色合金打造，在常見的描述中，它就像一個比例失調的矮人和一隻巨型甲蟲的結合。機<span class=\"GramE\">仆</span>內部的空間足夠容納1<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">噸的載重和一個內建的艙室，兩個中型生物能夠從這裡控制它</span>——<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">並帶來一場勢不可擋的毀滅。</span><br /><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">關於機</span><span class=\"GramE\">仆</span>來歷的傳說<span class=\"GramE\">更多僅</span>是猜測而非事實，其中通常會<span class=\"GramE\">提及異界的</span>存在，奧斯世界神秘的屏障峰，以及被稱為「<em>瘋子盧姆的機器（the Machine of Lum the Mad）</em>」<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">的相關裝置。關於這臺裝置的起源和操作的細節能夠在</span><span class=\"GramE\">一</span>本名為<em>《金屬之心（Mind of Metal）》</em><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">的書中尋得。這本書是一本</span><span class=\"GramE\">奇械師</span>的秘卷，由瘋子盧姆的後代盧姆大師（Lum the Maestro<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">）撰寫，當時她正在試圖重組被拆散已久的</span><span class=\"GramE\"><em>琉克歐</em></span><em>的非凡機</em><span class=\"GramE\"><em>仆</em></span><em>Mighty Servant of </em><span class=\"SpellE\"><em>Leuk</em></span><em>-O</em><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">。</span><br /><em><strong>危險同調</strong></em><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">。兩個生物能同時與機</span><span class=\"GramE\">仆</span>進行同調。如果第三個人試圖和機<span class=\"GramE\">仆</span>同調，則無事發生。<br /><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">機</span><span class=\"GramE\">仆</span>的控制艙室可以通過其背部的一扇艙門進入，當沒有生物與之同調時，這扇艙門很容易開啟。與這件神器同調需要兩個小時，可以作為長休的一部分進行。在此期間，你必須進入機<span class=\"GramE\">仆</span>的內部，除錯它的控制裝置。當駕駛員進行同調時，任何在機<span class=\"GramE\">仆</span>外部和其50<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">尺內的生物或建築都有</span>50%<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">可能在同調過程中被其毀滅鐵拳攻擊意外擊中一次。每當有一個生物試圖將自己與之同調時，都會發生這一過程。</span><br /><em><strong>控制機</strong></em><span class=\"GramE\"><em><strong>仆</strong></em></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">。當有任何生物與神器同調時，同調的生物能夠像打開其他們一樣輕鬆地打開艙門。其他生物則需要通過</span>DC25<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">的盜賊工具檢定才能打開艙門。一道對艙門施展的<em>@UUID[Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.Item.VC9nFuUxF7yptXK5]{敲擊術knock}</em>法術能夠讓艙門在施法者下個回合開始之前開啟。</span><br /><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">一個生物能夠以</span>10<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">尺移動力進出艙門。在機</span><span class=\"GramE\">仆</span>內部的生物和物件對源自外部的效應具有全掩護。內部的控制<span class=\"GramE\">艙能夠</span>讓內部的生物毫無阻擋地看到外面的景象。<br /><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">當你在機</span><span class=\"GramE\">仆</span>內部時，你能通過控制系統控制其行動。在你（每一個與之同調的生物）的回合中，你能以以下方式命令機<span class=\"GramE\">仆</span>：<br />·<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">打開或關閉艙門（不需要動作，</span><span class=\"GramE\">一</span>回合一次）<br />·<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">讓機</span><span class=\"GramE\">仆</span>移動最大為其速度的距離（不需要動作）<br />·<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">以一個動作，你</span><span class=\"GramE\">能命令機仆</span>執行其數據版中的動作或之外的其他動作。<br />·<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">當一個生物觸發來自機</span><span class=\"GramE\">仆</span>的藉機攻擊時，你能以你的反應動作命令機<span class=\"GramE\">仆</span>對該生物進行一次毀滅鐵拳攻擊。<br /><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">當沒有生物與之同調時，神器只是一件不會活動的物件。</span><br /><em><strong>械中幽靈</strong></em><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">。在迎來死亡時，強大的軍閥</span><span class=\"GramE\">琉克歐</span>的靈魂被吸入這臺神器之中，併成為能讓它活化的力量。機<span class=\"GramE\">仆</span>會採取特別是能造成破壞自行攻擊和移動。每24<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">小時一次，由</span>DM<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">決定，無人駕駛的機</span><span class=\"GramE\">仆</span>會進行一次這樣的動作。<br /><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">如果機</span><span class=\"GramE\">仆</span>失去其一半或一半以上的生命值，每個與之同調的生物必須成功通過DC20<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">的感知豁免，否則被魅惑長達</span>24<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">小時。</span><span class=\"GramE\">當因此</span>被魅惑時，生物會縱情破壞，試圖毀滅一切建築並攻擊一切機<span class=\"GramE\">仆</span>視野中未與之同調的生物。如果可能的話，它會盡量操作機<span class=\"GramE\">仆</span>，並從那些威脅到神器的生物開始攻擊。<br /><em><strong>自毀</strong></em><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">。通過拉動一系列的槓桿並按下按鈕，機</span><span class=\"GramE\">仆</span>的兩位駕駛員能夠令它自爆。當機<span class=\"GramE\">仆</span>的駕駛員與之同調時，自毀密碼並不會<span class=\"GramE\">被透露</span>給他們。如果密碼被找到（由DM<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">決定如何發現），則需要與之同調的駕駛員從機</span><span class=\"GramE\">仆</span>內部，在連續三回合耗費他們的動作輸入密碼。但是，如果駕駛員們開始輸入自毀密碼的過程，機<span class=\"GramE\">仆</span>會<span class=\"GramE\">使用其械中</span>幽靈特性並令兩位駕駛員相互對立。<br /><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">如果船員們成功輸入了密碼，第三輪結束時，機</span><span class=\"GramE\">仆</span>會自爆。以機<span class=\"GramE\">仆</span>為中心半徑100<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">尺球狀區域內每個生物必須進行</span>DC25<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">敏捷豁免檢定。豁免失敗的情況下，生物會受到</span>87<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">（</span>25d6<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">）力場傷害，</span>87<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">（</span>25d6<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">）閃電傷害和</span>87<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">（</span>25d6<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">）雷鳴傷害。豁免失敗的情況下，該生物受到一半的傷害。範圍內的物件和建築受到三倍傷害，機</span><span class=\"GramE\">仆</span>體內的生物會立即被殺死，並不會留下任何遺骸。<br /><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">自毀不會立即破壞機</span><span class=\"GramE\">仆</span>。相反，2d6<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">日後，它的部分：左臂，左腿，右臂，右腿，上部軀幹和下部軀幹會在爆炸</span>1000<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">英里內的隨機地點從天空落下。如果這些部分被帶到彼此的</span>5<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">尺內，它們會重新連線並再度組裝成機</span><span class=\"GramE\">仆</span>。<br /><em><strong>破壞機</strong></em><span class=\"GramE\"><em><strong>仆</strong></em></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">。機</span><span class=\"GramE\">仆</span>能夠被兩種方式破壞。在其自毀之後，它散落的碎片能夠在它古代奧爾<span class=\"GramE\">曼</span>人創造者的一座鍛造神廟中被融化。如果機<span class=\"GramE\">仆</span>與盧姆的機器相撞，兩件神器都會在規模範圍和傷害是機<span class=\"GramE\">仆</span>自毀的三倍的爆炸中毀滅。</p><div><div><p class=\"MsoNormal\"> </p></div></div></div>",
